症嘅親人，係咩心態？<br />\n係覺得親人好想繼續受苦？定純粹自己好唔捨得？"},{"pid":"4ed31d2a6a3ccabd0ca9faf4bdffe589b6deef79","tid":209230,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離post有個回覆好啱聽<br />\n而家醫療進步左，人嘅心態都變左，開始唔識得接受 生老病死 係人生必經之路<br />\n有時我都會諗，死R爛R要人地捐肝捐腎去救一個醫返都有無盡後遺症嘅親人，係咩心態？<br />\n係覺得親人好想繼續受苦？定純粹自己好唔捨得？</blockquote><br />\n睇下咩角度啫<br />\n<br />\n各方都有自己觀點睇件事<br />\n<br />\n有人借勢推動捐器官<br />\n<br />\n有人借勢搏上位<br />\n<br />\n有人得到案例經驗<br />\n<br />\nEtc..."},{"pid":"f862a281e6942514bf35892be6600e5f747212f8","tid":209230,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"大愛撚的結果"},{"pid":"c040adb6728ceb833e8bec9209595d1c1c0cb310","tid":209230,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"睇完呢單我就算捐都係死左先捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6082270a06a44c2b4dbc4efd18e3057f9f83456d","tid":209230,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完呢單我就算捐都係死左先捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCannot agree anymore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以現在醫學技術都係算鳩掃吧啦"},{"pid":"99c8a046e48e6a07efc3530fa2ef736521a4e2d1","tid":209230,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"Jack d 口duck la ching"},{"pid":"4552dfc067cbefa1b67cf37541270e1d7702abf1","tid":209230,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"670581ec0e1de376b4d1155094c776ea231519f9","tid":209230,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離post有個回覆好啱聽<br />\n而家